Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 是斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道了马尔科参加歼灭战的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有新情报会告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统辅佐官和人质没什么分别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往好的方向想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以伺机要了他的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传话给上校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡现在还徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你告诉我有关伊修瓦尔的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊修瓦尔发生了那样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对我这么个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她全部都说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术师是真理的追寻者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 对身边事浑然不觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校他已经想到了达成目的之后的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达成目的之后么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你恢复了原来的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要干些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吃温莉做的苹果派
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我脑子里除了恢复原来的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都装不下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先跑到婆婆还有师傅他们那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们「我们恢复身体了！」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为给大家添了不少麻烦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都会笑着迎接我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以看到大家的笑容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然情况不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我现在恢复些精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候我们的炼金术无法发动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时 地面上好像也发动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 那个女孩还有斯卡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 只有他们能用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有什么玄机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人的炼金术 肯定有我们不知道的要素
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离到头儿还早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个豆丁女走了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一早就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找遍整个中央市？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.76,0:04:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还没任何线索？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有线索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慰问品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要那种登着很多小姐的杂志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不在的时候不要偷懒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就要走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去尝尝西部的名菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我好好留守
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃 变强壮 变大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留守期间要好好保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利上士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔曼准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没出发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来还上校东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短暂的中央市勤务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上士你是南方司令部是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 正相反的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北方司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见啦 菲利上士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打搅了 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来拿忘记的东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡还在徘徊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真得注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身手好的护卫也走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请一定要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你辛苦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉跟错了人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得错了就一枪嘣了他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们当时的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在容许范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉你真是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见了 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:07:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作 不要偷懒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卒被…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您喜好真特别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,象也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我觉得非常光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连车都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上马…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我脑子笨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在士官学校真是辛苦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如您所愿 至死相随
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王后也被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…离将军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还早着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这种小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在找带着这种小猫的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请无视那边的异型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 完全没有黑白猫的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们也许已经不在中央市了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢仔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是新国的炼丹术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会问一下其他的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话我真不想欠上校你的人情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 说起欠债
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快还钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看前面！前面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少钱来的？500先士？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是520先士！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想混过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记这么清楚干啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样怎么能成为大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是得先欠着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等上校当上总统了再还
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听谁说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍克艾中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括有关伊修瓦尔的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢仔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱就让你先欠着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我肯定会要回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到时候我再管你借点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等实现了民主主义再还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等还上这笔 我还借
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再约定点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 我如果不活得长点还不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许让中尉担心！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你送我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来好晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我好等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀 这不是罗伊嘛 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来不错啊 瓦涅莎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见 罗伊少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好 克莉斯玛斯（Christmas）夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 很糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以跑来散散心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大病初愈 酒就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来点特别的吧 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉曼阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央市的克莉斯玛斯女士来的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 不要把机密电话的号码告诉普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 我还老当益壮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把年纪还有人指名哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能至死守护少主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此狼狈相…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这还算姚家选上的人么 真不害臊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好歹是伤员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你说住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胳膊…没了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻丫头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和兰芳说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要给她介绍个好机械铠技师的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的好意心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要更多协助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机械铠的事情我们自己想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我们怎么能坐视不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人看到兰芳的脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不能让你们的朋友再卷入麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我孙女捡回一条命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是什么值得被人感谢的医生…啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺克斯医生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是谢谢您了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你们都赶快给我走人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没好到可以长期收留你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝陛下的身体每况愈下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要早日夺回少主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着长生不老之法回国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着吧 魔窟的住民们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的救命之恩我永生难忘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺克斯医生 真是谢谢您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会儿我竟然又扮起医生来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公你还好么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来附近办事所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也瘦了许多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作忙么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 还是老样子每天对着尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这个礼拜治疗了两个活人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这样的人还能救人命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 我决定要当医生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道爸爸自从伊修瓦尔归来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直非常痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但爸爸并没有放弃行医
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常喜欢爸爸当医生的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然味道可能不怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝杯咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 真够乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们趁爸爸冲咖啡的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮他收拾一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若真有神存在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就请放我一马吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是也能祈求与家人一起喝咖啡的幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样伊修瓦尔就完全在国军的管辖之内了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了啊 金布利少校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石功效如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以无视等价交换实现超乎想象的炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打一份详细的报告上来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头就还回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要干什么 金布利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道贤者之石存在的就你们几个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来吧 金布利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被释放了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要多问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是上面的命令么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你杀了五名士官却没被判死刑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你耍了什么手段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.10,0:17:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人德所至吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了 你这个炸弹魔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然释放你这种变态
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上头的人究竟怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看守老弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长久以来给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别再回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一点小礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊 给我拿下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金布利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一件无聊的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妨带回去给你孩子玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见 金布利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你出狱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们命令的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 有活要交给我么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:18:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得马尔科医生么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个制造贤者之石的研究人员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个马尔科跑了…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还没搞清
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看守的合成兽少了一只
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尔科是擅长生体炼成的炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以尸体可能是替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有更麻烦的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能是和一个叫斯卡的伊修瓦尔人一起逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这参与伊修瓦尔歼灭战的红莲之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是从我手上逃脱的伊修瓦尔人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就更难以原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到斯卡就杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但马尔科要带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了这点小事把我搞出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果抓到马尔科
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:20:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了以儆效尤 让你从地图上抹消一个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份工作不赖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真够过火的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没用了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果消灭一个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个可能不太够用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也是用伊修瓦尔人做的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用马尔科医生的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那群研究石头的人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很过火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有些事情要问清楚你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫金布利的炼金术师的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我哥留下的研究书
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些地方不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究书？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥生前曾经说过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:21:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「这个国家的炼金术很古怪」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里应该有记录
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是有能力的炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以能解读吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家的炼金术很古怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老兄 那个小姑娘回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡先生你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 同伴又增加了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫马尔科
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.69,0:21:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是制造贤者之石 令伊修瓦尔一族灭绝的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石？就是长生不老啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.51,0:21:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尔科先生 你知道石头的制作方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做的呀 请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别问了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要追求那种东西
